<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Credential Code – GCEX Proof of Reserve</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        color: #222;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 36px 40px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444;
      }
      .otp-box {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        background: #f0f4ff;
        border: 1px solid #c5d0f0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        padding-top: 16px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Your Verification Code</h1>
      <p>Use the code below to verify your identity for <strong>GCEX Proof of Reserve</strong>. Do not share this code with anyone.</p>

      <div class="otp-box">{{code}}</div>

      <p>This code is valid for a limited time. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>

      <p class="note">This is an automated message from GCEX. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
